1. *Spavanje* je odličan način da se oporaviš nakon napornog dana. (Sleeping is a great way to recover after a tiring day.)

2. Ona voli da sluša muziku dok *spava*. (She likes to listen to music while sleeping.)

3. On je potpuno zaboravio da se *spava*. (He completely forgot to sleep.)

4. Ona je *spavala* dok je čula nečije korake. (She was sleeping while she heard someone's footsteps.)

5. Oni su često *spavali* do podne. (They often slept until noon.)

6. Ona je imala loše *spavanje* prethodne noći. (She had a bad sleep the night before.)